                | From our gourmet restaurant to our outstanding amenities and exciting events, we&apos;re dedicated to making every moment of your stay exceptional.
        .row
          .col-12.col-md-12.col-lg-4
            .card.text-center.bg-white.pb-2
              .card-body.text-dark
                .img-area.mb-4
                  img.img-fluid(src='/assets/img/Restaurant.jpg' alt='')
                h5.room-titletext
                  span R
                  | estaurant
                p.lead
                  | Savor the artistry of our culinary team at our restaurant. From gourmet breakfasts to delectable dinners, every dish is a masterpiece of flavor, prepared with the freshest ingredients to satisfy your palate.
                button.btn.btn-primary.text-white Learn More
          .col-12.col-md-12.col-lg-4
