                  | Indulge in a world of relaxation with our top-notch amenities. Dive into our exquisite pool, rejuvenate at the spa, or maintain your fitness routine in our well-equipped gym. We&apos;ve thought of every detail to ensure your well-being.
                button.btn.btn-primary.text-white Learn More
          .col-12.col-md-12.col-lg-4
            .card.text-center.bg-white.pb-2
              .card-body.text-dark
                .img-area.mb-4
                  img.img-fluid(src='/assets/img/EventHall.jpg' alt='')
