                  span E
                  | vents
                p.lead
                  | Join us for an array of exciting events that add an extra layer of excitement to your stay. From live music nights to themed parties, we create memorable moments that make your visit to ARUGA truly unforgettable.
                button.btn.btn-primary.text-white Learn More
